OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FA bonfire was lit a day early after
OL,7,Fpolice began an operation to remove a
OL,8,Freplica of a mosque from the top of
OL,9,Fthe pyre.
OL,11,FThe PSNI said it had launched a
OL,12,F"significant and complex policing
OL,13,Foperation to remove a hate display"
OL,14,Ffrom the top of the bonfire in
OL,15,FMoygashel, Co Tyrone.
OL,17,FPolice said the operation was at an
OL,18,Fadvanced stage when the bonfire was
OL,19,Flit and "offending material" would
OL,20,Fhave been removed and seized as
OL,21,Fevidence once the site was secured.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@cO]{D@IOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/20
