PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FA 56-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith incitement to hatred, police
OL,8,Fsaid. He is due to appear before
OL,9,FDungannon Magistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,11,FA PSNI said in a statement earlier on
OL,12,FThursday evening: "The display on the
OL,13,FMoygashel bonfire is being treated as
OL,14,Fa hate-motivated criminal offence."
OL,16,FChief Superintendent Norman Haslett
OL,17,Fsaid: "Hate crime has no place in our
OL,18,Fsociety and will not be tolerated.
OL,26,@tD@SOUvD@cO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"That is why tonight we commenced a
OL,7,Fproactive policing operation to take
OL,8,Faction and remove the hate display
OL,9,Ffrom Moygashel Bonfire.
OL,11,F"Before police arrival the bonfire was
OL,12,Fset alight a day in advance to prevent
OL,13,Fremoval of the criminal material.
OL,15,F"Where there is evidence that offences
OL,16,Fhave been committed, we will take
OL,17,Frobust action.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
