OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"As part of our ongoing investigation,
OL,7,Fa 56-year-old man has been charged
OL,8,Fwith incitement to hatred. As is
OL,9,Fnormal procedure, all charges are
OL,10,Freviewed by the Public Prosecution
OL,11,FService."
OL,13,FThe model, visible on top of the pyre
OL,14,Fin Moygashel on Thursday, has been
OL,15,Fwidely condemned by political parties,
OL,16,Freligious leaders and a human rights
OL,17,Fgroup.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/20
