PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FArchbishop John McDowell and
OL,7,FArchbishop Eamon Martin issued a joint
OL,8,Fstatement describing the replica
OL,9,Fmosque atop the bonfire as "grossly
OL,10,Foffensive" and urged people to express
OL,11,Fcompassion to those from other
OL,12,Freligions.
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,15,Fhas described it as a "sickening and
OL,16,Fcowardly act of intimidation".
OL,18,FIn a social media post, Mr Benn said:
OL,19,F"The placement of a replica mosque on
OL,20,Fthe Moygashel bonfire is a sickening
OL,21,Fand cowardly act of intimidation.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@JO]wD@WOUxD@]O]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"This is not about tradition, and in
OL,7,Fno way does it represent the vast
OL,8,Fmajority of people in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,F"We must stand united and completely
OL,11,Freject such hatred."
OL,13,FArchbishop McDowell and Archbishop
OL,14,FMartin said the targeting of the
OL,15,FMuslim community "through crude
OL,16,Fsymbols and threats of violence by
OL,17,Fsinister forces" undermines gospel
OL,18,Fprinciples of respect and compassion,
OL,19,Fas well as freedom of religion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@TO]wD@ROUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
