FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"The placement of a replica mosque
OL,7,Fatop a bonfire is grossly offensive
OL,8,Fand raises tensions so soon after the
OL,9,Funrest that destroyed property and
OL,10,Fseverely impacted the lives of
OL,11,Findividuals and families," they said.
OL,13,F"Likewise, we should be appalled at
OL,14,Fthe provocative denigration of symbols
OL,15,Fassociated with faiths that are
OL,16,Fsincerely held by others.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/20
