PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"We urge Christians, and all people of
OL,7,Fgood will, to reflect carefully on
OL,8,Ftheir actions which can ignite
OL,9,Fviolence against innocent people, all
OL,10,Fof whom are made in God's image and
OL,11,Fare therefore worthy of respect and
OL,12,Fcompassion.
OL,14,F"We want to assure our Muslim fellow
OL,15,Fcitizens and those who are living and
OL,16,Fworking here of the goodwill and
OL,17,Frespect of the majority of people
OL,18,Fhere."
OL,20,FThe bonfire site has attracted
OL,21,Fcontroversy in previous years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/20
