PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FLast year, there was condemnation
OL,7,Fafter effigies of migrants in a boat
OL,8,Fwere burned on the Moygashel fire.
OL,10,FThe DUP said effigies should not be
OL,11,Fplaced on bonfires.
OL,13,FA party spokesperson said: "The DUP
OL,14,Fsupports the right of people to
OL,15,Fexpress lawful political opinions,
OL,16,Feven where those opinions are
OL,17,Fcontroversial or unpopular.
OL,19,F"Where the law is broken, it should be
OL,20,Fenforced.
OL,26,@uD@\OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"Where views are expressed lawfully,
OL,7,Fthey should not be censored simply
OL,8,Fbecause some find them offensive.
OL,10,F"The 11th of July bonfires are a
OL,11,Fhistoric and cultural tradition
OL,12,Fstretching back to the fires lit to
OL,13,Fwelcome the arrival of King William
OL,14,FIII.
OL,16,F"These should be positive cultural
OL,17,Fcelebrations. We support those within
OL,18,Four community that wish to celebrate
OL,19,Ftheir culture by continuing with that
OL,20,Ftradition in a peaceful way.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"The placing of flags, effigies or
OL,7,Fother items on bonfires is not part of
OL,8,Fthat tradition and should not take
OL,9,Fplace."
OL,11,FUlster Unionist Party leader Jon
OL,12,FBurrows has called for the "immediate
OL,13,Fremoval of the offensive display".
OL,15,FHe said: "Bonfires are an important
OL,16,Fcultural tradition for many within the
OL,17,Funionist community, and there will be
OL,18,Fmany peaceful and respectful bonfires
OL,19,Facross Northern Ireland over the
OL,20,Fcoming days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]tD@\OUuD@aO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"However, that tradition is undermined
OL,7,Fwhen bonfires are used to intimidate,
OL,8,Fprovoke or demean others.
OL,10,F"There can be no place for placing any
OL,11,Fplace of worship on a bonfire and
OL,12,Fsetting it alight. It is simply wrong.
OL,14,F"Sadly, images of this bonfire will
OL,15,Fonce again travel around the world,
OL,16,Fdamaging Northern Ireland's reputation
OL,17,Fand playing into the hands of critics
OL,18,Fof unionist and loyalist culture."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
