CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FIn a statement on social media, the
OL,7,FMoygashel Bonfire Association said it
OL,8,Fhad "noted the predicable fury in
OL,9,Frespect of the act of political
OL,10,Fprotest at our bonfire site this year".
OL,12,FThe statement said: "This year we have
OL,13,Ffocused on an issue of significant
OL,14,Fpublic interest.
OL,26,@pD@EOUrD@fO]tD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,F"Our display may well shock, offend or
OL,7,Foutrage others, but nonetheless it is
OL,8,Fan exercise in our rights under
OL,9,FArticle 10 of the ECHR and we note
OL,10,Fwith some irony that it is the ECHR
OL,11,Fwhich has so often paved the way for
OL,12,Fmass illegal immigration and a failure
OL,13,Fto deport foreign criminals who have
OL,14,Fcome here unlawfully, that also now
OL,15,Fprotects our right to protest in
OL,16,Frobust terms against that.
OL,18,F"If there was no uncontrolled illegal
OL,19,Fmass immigration, we would have no
OL,20,Fneed to protest on this issue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FIt added: "Our display expressly does
OL,7,FNOT target any individual. We make
OL,8,Fthat very clear.
OL,10,F"Our opposition is not to people, but
OL,11,Frather to ideology and Government
OL,12,Fpolicy.
OL,14,F"Once this is appreciated, then it is
OL,15,Fvery clear this is no more and no less
OL,16,Fthan an act of protest, which is
OL,17,Flawful protected expression."
OL,19,FFermanagh and South Tyrone Sinn Fein
OL,20,FMLA Colm Gildernew described the
OL,21,Fdisplay on the bonfire as "deplorable".
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@]O]{D@brr}D@[OU}D@
OL,26,AfO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/20
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
