FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FHe said: "The signage and effigy on
OL,7,Fthe Moygashel bonfire is a clear hate
OL,8,Fcrime.
OL,10,F"This is fuelled by hate and those
OL,11,Fthat seek to bring division to our
OL,12,Fcommunities.
OL,14,F"There is no place in our society for
OL,15,Fracism, and it is the responsibility
OL,16,Fof all political representatives and
OL,17,Fcommunity leaders to stand against it.
OL,19,F"The PSNI must investigate this as a
OL,20,Fmatter of urgency to remove this
OL,21,Fdisgraceful display."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/20
