PN,41518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FAlliance Party councillor Eddie Roofe
OL,7,Fdescribed the bonfire as "hateful and
OL,8,Fdeeply offensive".
OL,10,FHe said: "The placing of this model on
OL,11,Ftop of the bonfire is utterly
OL,12,Fabhorrent.
OL,14,F"Those responsible seek only to instil
OL,15,Ffear and spread hatred towards a
OL,16,Fspecific group of people who call
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland their home, and it
OL,18,Fmust be removed immediately."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@QO]rD@JOUvD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/20
