FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1783720151
OL,3,CBonfire with mosque replica placed on
OL,4,Ctop set alight
OL,6,FEleventh night bonfires will be lit
OL,7,Facross Northern Ireland on Friday,
OL,8,FSaturday and Sunday evenings ahead of
OL,9,Fthe Orange Order's July 12 parades on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,FWhile most of the bonfires pass off
OL,13,Fwithout incident, several have become
OL,14,Fthe focus of contention due to the
OL,15,Fplacing of flags, effigies and
